  "siteName": "创业邦",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\">\n   <p style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503365694\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5720562390158173\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1138\" style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.034em;width:100%;visibility:visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/03KNO9Fib2w53kOxJIdDgM3UDsGtFELNY6DO5mZ4BdQyW7zYotB7uz1RG5DKsIVyBHNKY5HeIOrW4P0EHbzIpEA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"307\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"312\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=653150de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w53kOxJIdDgM3UDsGtFELNY6DO5mZ4BdQyW7zYotB7uz1RG5DKsIVyBHNKY5HeIOrW4P0EHbzIpEA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">来源丨</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">硅星人（ID：</span><span style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">Si-Planet</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">）</span></p>\n   <p style=\"outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">作者丨</span><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq9721if\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 16px; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mhofhq9721if&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Yoky</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"outline:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">图源丨Midjourney</span></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97uqi\">OpenAI的动作比所有人想象的都要快。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97u3p\">上周二，OpenAI完成重组。其中一个重要变化是：彻底取消了与微软的排他性协议，结束了Azure长达六年的云服务独占模式。此前，OpenAI所有模型的训练、推理与部署都必须优先选择Azure，微软还享有优先购买权。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97tj9\">宣布与Azure“分手”后不到一周，OpenAI便火速宣布了与AWS的战略合作——双方达成一项价值380亿美元的云计算协议，OpenAI将全面接入AWS的算力资源：数十万张最新一代英伟达GPU，外加数千万颗正在部署的CPU。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq9715jx\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这种“无缝衔接”的速度瞬间引发热议。毕竟在过去很长一段时间里，OpenAI与微软的关系都十分“微妙”，双方不合的传闻屡见不鲜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971onb\">在OpenAI风靡全球之后，无数新的“伯乐”涌来，OpenAI快速成长为让所有硅谷巨头都倍感威胁的公司，在某些方面也成了微软的直接竞争对手。这些都让他们的关系变得尴尬，甚至在整个2025年两位核心人物并未同时出席过公开活动。在这次深度对话之前，仅在今年5月微软Build大会中，Altman通过视频连线匆匆而过，发言时间甚至没有马斯克多。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97zri\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这次与AWS的闪电合作，似乎坐实了外界的猜测。但真相果真如此吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq977n5\">上周日，Sam Altman和Satya Nadella久违地同框，一起录制了一档视频播客。主持人Brad Gerstner开门见山地问道：“ChatGPT或GPT-6不会出现在亚马逊或谷歌的云上，对吗？”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100136396\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.548\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"546\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;display:block;letter-spacing:inherit;\" width=\"996\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"317\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=059087b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjopKOlhibRBLlgncMGwx4BiaFAPY98hBzNFZdk5dcPdMUQgr1g0GMqXEJqoKdHGJ8rN5oPHrZ0jY6JUMPP7aXfRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n  <figure>\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971c7\">Altman立刻否认并澄清：“不是这样的。”他解释说，双方合作的核心是运行在Azure上的“无状态API”，但这部分并非完全排他，且协议有明确期限（至2030年）。同时他强调：“其他产品和模型，我们也会在不同的平台上发布。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97sax\">这几乎是对独占权问题的正面回应。而全程在场的Nadella，用他的沉默与在场本身，为这场澄清作了最有力的背书。在这场播客中，尽管两人的关系不如“蜜月期”那般热络，但至少有一点可以确定：他们又重新站到了一起，以一种更成熟、更务实的方式，缔结了新的同盟。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971dz3\">从OpenAI近期的种种动作来看，这家公司正告别野蛮生长的第一阶段。而在下一个阶段的朋友圈里，微软仍然是最重要的那一个。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\">\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502705851\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"45\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e93a19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zPEErlmM1icwAxnc0Bfu3icv2I49pcxADF7lYww8vNML5TkajhGu2m1NA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofo98pz2e\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhofo99e1oft\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">今天的AWS，不是昨天的Azure</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971p0h\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">要理解OpenAI与微软如今这种的新型同盟，我们必须首先厘清一个核心问题：</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">OpenAI的战略重心，已经发生了根本性的转移。</span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97p6m\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">外界之所以对OpenAI与AWS的合作感到震惊，是因为他们仍停留在“上一个时代”的惯性思维里。在那个时代，OpenAI的唯一焦点是</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">模型的训练与创造</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">。为了炼成GPT-3、GPT-4这样史无前例的“巨兽”，它需要一个能够提供海量、稳定且高度集成算力的“专属锻造炉”。Azure，几乎是当时唯一的选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971nkt\">对于微软而言，与OpenAI的独家深度绑定是一次堪称世纪级的战略投资。通过支撑OpenAI的训练，Azure不仅在技术上完成了对超大规模AI负载的深度优化，一举成为全球公认“最懂AI的智能云”；更在市场上，凭借这块金字招牌，甩开追兵，稳稳坐上了全球云市场第二的宝座。可以说，上一个阶段，是OpenAI与Azure围绕“训练”这一核心目标，构建的深度共生、互相成就的独占时代。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503365693\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/03KNO9Fib2w53kOxJIdDgM3UDsGtFELNYuCxEibrbkeC1kU5arIvSrkTibWBtw2iaTZdB61Uyej6g4x3CPZYz9zYSw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"302\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"307\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0ef1aa87&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F03KNO9Fib2w53kOxJIdDgM3UDsGtFELNYuCxEibrbkeC1kU5arIvSrkTibWBtw2iaTZdB61Uyej6g4x3CPZYz9zYSw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq9715r2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">然而，当模型本身已经足够强大，游戏的规则就变了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971rmi\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">进入下一个阶段，OpenAI的棋局不再仅仅是“如何把模型做得更大”，而是“如何让模型无处不在”</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">。</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">正如Sam Altman在播客中反复强调的，未来的重点在于CodexAI对编程世界的颠覆，以及由此催生的、能够深入千家万户的全新消费级硬件。这些目标的本质，是大规模的应用普及。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq972061\">这是Altman在如此公开场合，又一次明确表达了对创造全新硬件的浓厚兴趣和意愿。这表明OpenAI的野心远不止于软件和云端，而是要定义下一代人机交互的物理载体。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971kou\">大规模普及意味着什么？意味着不能再将所有鸡蛋放在一个篮子里。它要求OpenAI必须成为一个平台无关、无处不在的“AI水电煤”。它需要拥抱更广阔的生态，需要出现在开发者和用户最熟悉、最便捷的任何地方：无论是Azure，是AWS，还是未来的Google Cloud。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97232n\">所以AWS的意义，与当年的Azure截然不同。一个是用来“炼丹”的，一个是用来“卖药”的；一个关乎技术突破，一个关乎商业触达。这不是背叛，而是OpenAI从“模型研发实验室”向“全球AI平台公司”进化的必然转变。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971vds\">所以今天无论是OpenAI与甲骨文在算力层面的合作，还是AWS同时也为Anthropic提供云算力成为其核心的训练伙伴，并计划使用Trainium和Inferentia芯片来训练、部署Claude下一代基础模型，都并不稀奇。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971p38\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">毕竟旧时代需要一个最强的伙伴，新时代则需要一个更大的“朋友圈”。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;\">\n   <div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502705850\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"45\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9f561975&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w5wrEGVRwwiaPQcjibpiahYT0zSsWdBUSJRaL8xxhHssPefRrhSRCKFFTvyO0oNl4HVrDTxA2PCXqv1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97111s\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofpkniah2\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mhofpknz1fgz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">打破英伟达神话</span></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97a7o\">在更多合纵连横到来之前，这场播客透露的信息，或许要等“第二个AWS”、“第三个AWS”出现，外界才会真正读懂。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97206p\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">大部分人关注他们说了什么，更值得思考的是：为什么在这个节点，他们要坐在一起，以同盟的姿态对外发声。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97bf4\">上周几乎成为了硅谷极具动荡的一周，OpenAI刚刚宣布重组，英伟达用GTC再次轰炸科技圈，而Meta、Google、微软几家巨头连续发完财报之后，在这场播客中，Sam Altman和Satya Nadella几乎回应了OpenAI和微软合作的一切问题，同时也暴露出了双方更大的野心。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971ap\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">当主持人Brad Gerstner将话题抛向当前全球公认的难题：“算力稀缺”时，一直表现得沉稳、顾全大局的Satya Nadella，终于不再“端水”，抛出了第一个“暴论”：</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">未来的算力，一定是过剩的。</span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">真正的瓶颈并非GPU芯片本身，而是部署这些算力的物理环境：包括数据中心的建设速度、能源供应、以及冷却系统。他强调，建造足够的数据中心并为其提供能源，才是通往AGI道路上更艰巨的挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97bxm\">这个回答颇为意外。更有意思的是Sam Altman的反应——他不仅没有反驳，反而迅速跟进，从另一个角度强化了这一观点。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97ljg\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">根据播客内容，Altman承认，为了实现AGI，他们需要“多到令人难以置信的算力”，但他话锋一转，明确指出：“</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">总有一天，算力一定会过剩——至于是两三年后，还是五六年后，我说不准，但这肯定会发生，而且可能会多次发生。比如，如果大规模、极低成本的新型能源突然上线，签了长期合约的公司就会被“烧惨”。</span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971u8\">Nadella紧接着补充道：“我认为Sam刚才提到的一点其实外界谈得还不够多：比如，OpenAI在推理层面（inferencestack）针对GPU所做的优化。我们常常谈论摩尔定律带来的硬件性能提升，但实际上，软件层面的效率改进才是呈现出更强指数级增长的部分。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503365691\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55390625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"320\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5f10e30&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F03KNO9Fib2w53kOxJIdDgM3UDsGtFELNYbicPQW9rr5dehZISJFztHAf25homSWser5tmniaAxHWmxglT5EsQoutQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq974os\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">这番表态颇为微妙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971h7p\">要知道，在过去的几年里，英伟达不仅是OpenAI最核心的GPU供应商，双方更将建立更紧密的合作关系。根据此前报道，双方已达成或正在推进宏大的战略伙伴关系，有消息称计划部署一个高达10吉瓦（gigawatts）的NVIDIA AI超级计算机，首批系统预计在2026年上线，整个项目的投资金额可能超过1000亿美元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq9718l\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">在这样的背景下，Altman和Nadella却不约而同地“轻化GPU的重要性”：一个强调基建瓶颈，一个强调软件优化，这绝非随口一说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97tza\">Nadella和Altman的言论，本质上是在向市场传递一个新信号：GPU固然重要，但它只是拼图的一块。真正稀缺且难以复制的，是将数百万个GPU高效、稳定地整合在一起的超大规模数据中心、全球能源调度能力和系统工程能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq971d1k\">他们试图将价值链的重心，从“芯片制造”拉回到“平台服务与系统集成”上，强调微软作为“基建狂魔”的不可替代性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq97rax\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">很显然，尽管这一周硅谷发生了诸多大事，但GTC仍然是重中之重。英伟达在大会上展示的技术路线图和产品布局，再次点燃了市场对“GPU稀缺性”的狂热情绪。而OpenAI和微软选择在此刻联袂发声，</span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">不仅是为了回应外界对他们合作关系的质疑，而是为了抢在英伟达叙事彻底固化之前，重新定义AI产业的价值分配逻辑。</span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 16px;margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mhofhq9716dz\">事实上，OpenAI没有抛弃微软，也从未完全押注英伟达，新局刚开，诸君别急。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度解析 OpenAI 与微软关系新动态，指出其从独占走向多元合作，并揭示双方联手挑战英伟达在 AI 算力领域主导地位的战略意图。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度解析 OpenAI 与微软关系新动态，指出其从独占走向多元合作，并揭示双方联手挑战英伟达在 AI 算力领域主导地位的战略意图。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了 OpenAI、微软与英伟达之间复杂且动态的商业科技关系。首先，文章澄清了 OpenAI 与微软并非外界所传的“分手”，而是从过去的独占模式走向一种更成熟、务实的合作关系。OpenAI 与 AWS 的战略合作被解读为其战略重心从单纯的模型训练转向大规模应用普及的必然，旨在成为一个平台无关、无处不在的“AI 水电煤”，而微软的 Azure 仍是其核心的 AI 训练与部署平台。其次，文章重点揭示了 Sam Altman 和 Satya Nadella 在近期播客中共同强调“未来算力一定会过剩”的观点。这并非偶然，而是 OpenAI 和微软联手，试图在英伟达 GTC 大会后，重新定义 AI 产业的价值分配逻辑，将价值链的重心从“芯片制造”拉回到“平台服务与系统集成”，从而挑战英伟达在 AI 算力领域的叙事主导权，凸显微软作为“基建狂魔”的不可替代性。",
